column5: Total Hours on the Water - 6  Total Fish Landed - 7  Largest Smallmouth - 17"  Largest Largemouth - 15" X2  Hottest Bait - Plastic Crayfish Texas Rigged & Texas Rigged Worm  All pics self timed once again. Couldn't get my fishing protege to join me on this trip.         Hopefully another report coming within a weeks time. Looks like a lot of rain may be coming our way.
